Package beamline.models.algorithms

Class StreamMiningAlgorithm<T,​K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • beamline.models.algorithms.StreamMiningAlgorithm<T,​K>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the consumed events
    K - the type of the responses produced by the mining algorithm
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.reactivex.rxjava3.functions.Consumer<T>
    public abstract class StreamMiningAlgorithm<T,​K>
extends Object
implements io.reactivex.rxjava3.functions.Consumer<T>
    This abstract class defines the root of the mining algorithms hierarchy. It is a Consumer of elements with type T that is capable of producing responses of a certain type K.
    Author:
    Andrea Burattin
